{"tid":1283893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］大家唔好中計 7月7號千祈唔好去西九派嘢","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T13:23:03.000Z","uid":18245,"like":114,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cca47866db165d62beb683fa4cb13eebfab0cd","tid":1283893,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:10:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>[時間唔多] 7月7日西九遊行想派野比大陸人</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1283681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1283681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你哋咁搞法，陣間激嬲啊爺就煩架啦。 成個6月又<strong>遊行</strong>又<strong>示威</strong>，仲要<strong>全球登報</strong>喺g20落啊爺面都唔夠，仲要衝擊立法會。<br />\n<br />\n依家你仲話要 spread去中華人民共和國？！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本人對此強烈譴責！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">陣間啊爺嬲起上嚟，真係踢走我哋出中國點算！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係度呼籲自古以嚟都愛國嘅連登巴絲絕對唔好參與呢啲外國勢力所組織嘅暴動！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b664e86699ab4f0beb3e109c9097df340229b219","tid":1283893,"uid":201604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:11:02.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"04f00ab44935231d246db7ef95713a7926e6d506","tid":1283893,"uid":127589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:11:55.000Z","msg":"梗係派反英抗暴leaflet啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"075b85e0ac525c6d991e7621e4fedca69e611ac7","tid":1283893,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"